{"tid":1018003,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"被指暗嘲大陸客「人傻錢多」　D&G 豬年T恤捲辱華風波","createTime":"2019-02-12T01:29:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-13T00:55:51.000Z","uid":39464,"like":271,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":129,"replies":[{"pid":"12e3cd11e02775ad511a0f65255cb1e54511eeb0","tid":1018003,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-12T01:29:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/DG-21_qzOY9_1200x0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2FDG-21_qzOY9_1200x0.png&h=a06e5a24&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n意大利時裝品牌Dolce &amp; Gabbana再次捲入「辱華」風波。該品牌在新年推出多款以豬作為主題的T恤，其中一款小豬手執一疊鈔票，即被質疑是暗嘲中國消費者「人傻錢多」。內地網民對此反應兩極，有人表明罷買，但亦有人認為不應過份解讀、對號入座。<br />\n<br />\n翻查D&amp;G官方網站，該款新年小豬T恤共有5款，每件盛惠2,900至3,500元人民幣。其中一款T恤上，小豬手拿品牌Logo及一疊鈔票，設計即引來關注。內地媒體紛引述網民質疑，這是品牌對中國文化的又一次扭曲詮釋，或暗指中國消費者「人傻錢多」。<br />\n<br />\n在微博上，事件亦引起不少內地網民討論。不少網民表明會拒絕購買D&amp;G的產品，但亦有人認為內地媒體是過份解讀：「真看不出辱華，媒體不要煽動民族情緒，請保持理性客觀！」<br />\n<br />\nD&amp;G去年亦曾爆出「辱華」風波，品牌去年11月上載宣傳短片，片中一名細眼方面的中國女模特兒，先後以笨拙的姿態，用筷子吃大碗意大利粉、意式薄餅（Pizza）及意式香炸甜卷（Cannolo），片段引起辱華爭議。網上截圖顯示，品牌創辦人之一的 Stefano Gabbana 在 Instagram（IG） 與網民就短片內容激辯時說「中國就是屎國」，引起軒然大波。<br />\n<br />\n爆出事件後，多位獲邀出席的內地明星如章子怡、黃曉明、陳坤、李冰冰和廸麗熱巴等，紛紛在微博亮出「祖國高於一切」、「我愛我的祖國」等口號，表明拒絕出席 D&amp;G 活動，原訂周三晚在上海舉行的時裝展最後被取消。 D&amp;G 中國代言人王俊凱及迪麗熱巴的工作室更分別發表聲明，宣佈與該公司解約。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/china/被指暗嘲大陸客-人傻錢多-d-g-豬年t恤捲辱華風波/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fchina%2F%E8%A2%AB%E6%8C%87%E6%9A%97%E5%98%B2%E5%A4%A7%E9%99%B8%E5%AE%A2-%E4%BA%BA%E5%82%BB%E9%8C%A2%E5%A4%9A-d-g-%E8%B1%AC%E5%B9%B4t%E6%81%A4%E6%8D%B2%E8%BE%B1%E8%8F%AF%E9%A2%A8%E6%B3%A2%2F&d=DoGI4G7aG2aFCjNgNSWIut8yddZnhMmQMHU13Um27G0%3D&h=6686a6dd\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fchina%2F%E8%A2%AB%E6%8C%87%E6%9A%97%E5%98%B2%E5%A4%A7%E9%99%B8%E5%AE%A2-%E4%BA%BA%E5%82%BB%E9%8C%A2%E5%A4%9A-d-g-%E8%B1%AC%E5%B9%B4t%E6%81%A4%E6%8D%B2%E8%BE%B1%E8%8F%AF%E9%A2%A8%E6%B3%A2%2F&h=f9b21768\" target=\"_blank\">https://thestandnews.com/china/被指暗嘲大陸客-人傻錢多-d-g-豬年t恤捲辱華風波/</a>"},{"pid":"351cb0fdce8826897836ceefb32e4dc3e5f4765a","tid":1018003,"uid":12208,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-12T01:30:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"88f1600e1693f3a064e43c0d29d6bcde51544b8a","tid":1018003,"uid":45788,"like":331,"dislike":1,"score":330,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-12T01:30:59.000Z","msg":"作賊心虛呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"15b0477d0cb2c238493701bf502149c9b927f8c6","tid":1018003,"uid":4942,"like":119,"dislike":3,"score":116,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-12T01:31:33.000Z","msg":"其實係媒體放大黎講吧？"},{"pid":"ac1b678ceecaefd39c1068c5074c52606fe708bb","tid":1018003,"uid":37661,"like":347,"dislike":2,"score":345,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-12T01:31:35.000Z","msg":"不少網民表明會拒絕購買D&amp;G的產品<br />\n<br />\n買唔起 =/= 拒絕買<br />\n<br />\n咪混為一談。"},{"pid":"9b7d252ad52992de238af1378644cc5c64bed594","tid":1018003,"uid":23931,"like":182,"dislike":0,"score":182,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-12T01:32:27.000Z","msg":"真係唔識欣賞<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n同女人街果啲有乜分別"},{"pid":"c2379ef20123383b1443017c271acc0de73564c4","tid":1018003,"uid":8048,"like":21,"dislike":0,"score":21,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-12T01:33:17.000Z","msg":"對號入座"},{"pid":"ed69d72f870312eb3bfc1e9c93631855a3961c39","tid":1018003,"uid":13374,"like":146,"dislike":0,"score":146,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-12T01:34:20.000Z","msg"